yaz (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Wayland-native screenshot capture (gnome-screenshot / grim / portal).
  * Annotation editor: rect, ellipse, arrow, line, pen, highlight, text, blur.
  * Full undo/redo for add, delete, move, crop.
  * Live property edits (color/width on selected items).
  * Delayed capture (3/5/10s) for hover screenshots.
  * Multi-monitor aware with correct fractional-scaling crop math.
  * Global keyboard-shortcut setup via gsettings.

